SCOPE: This MIT license covers ONLY this benchmark's own contributions — the code,
evaluation harness, frozen data splits, feature-engineering definitions, and
documentation in the `benchmark/` directory.

It does NOT cover the underlying mcPHASES dataset. mcPHASES is distributed by
PhysioNet under its own license and credentialed-access terms; obtain and use the
raw data under those terms directly from https://physionet.org/content/mcphases/ .
This benchmark redistributes no raw mcPHASES data — only code, subject-level split
indices, and derived evaluation artifacts.
